3 Days Ago In bid to control the rising heat, the party has called for an emergency NEC meeting. The meeting was announced by the acting National Secretary, Chief Victor T. Giadom. The meeting is scheduled to hold in Abuja on Tuesday, March 17, 2020. In his announcement, he said, "All NEC members to attend the emergency meeting in line with Article 25 (B) (II) of the constitution of the party."